    <p>Meanwhile, many established homes in Tooele City and Grantsville were built decades ago with electrical systems that were never designed for today's power demands. <a href="/services/panel-upgrades/">Panel upgrades</a>, circuit additions, and grounding updates are common projects we handle for homeowners looking to modernize their older properties safely and affordably.</p>
